{
  "book": "enos",
  "bookName": "Enos",
  "chapter": 1,
  "voice": {
    "provider": "elevenlabs",
    "voice_id": "lRf3yb6jZby4fn3q3Q7M",
    "model_id": "eleven_multilingual_v2",
    "settings": {
      "stability": 0.5,
      "similarity_boost": 0.75,
      "style": 0.35,
      "use_speaker_boost": true
    },
    "name": "Tony"
  },
  "pauses": {
    "line_ms": 180,
    "verse_ms": 500
  },
  "duration": 386.702,
  "lines": [
    {
      "start": 0.0,
      "end": 2.368,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Then behold, I, Enos, knowing my father",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 1
    },
    {
      "start": 2.548,
      "end": 4.127,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he was a just man\u2014",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 2
    },
    {
      "start": 4.307,
      "end": 6.257,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for he taught me in his language,",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 3
    },
    {
      "start": 6.437,
      "end": 9.456,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also in the nurture and admonition of the Lord\u2014",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 4
    },
    {
      "start": 9.636,
      "end": 12.097,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and blessed be the name of my God for it\u2014",
      "verse": "1:1",
      "lineIndex": 5
    },
    {
      "start": 12.777,
      "end": 16.121,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I will tell you of the wrestle which I had before God,",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 6
    },
    {
      "start": 16.301,
      "end": 18.809,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "before I received a remission of my sins.",
      "verse": "1:2",
      "lineIndex": 7
    },
    {
      "start": 19.489,
      "end": 22.183,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Behold, I went to hunt beasts in the forests;",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 9
    },
    {
      "start": 22.363,
      "end": 25.149,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the words which I had often heard my father speak",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 10
    },
    {
      "start": 25.329,
      "end": 26.954,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "concerning eternal life",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 11
    },
    {
      "start": 27.134,
      "end": 30.106,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the joy of the saints, sunk deep into my heart.",
      "verse": "1:3",
      "lineIndex": 12
    },
    {
      "start": 30.786,
      "end": 32.226,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And my soul hungered;",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 14
    },
    {
      "start": 32.406,
      "end": 34.542,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I kneeled down before my Maker,",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 15
    },
    {
      "start": 34.722,
      "end": 36.115,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I cried to him",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 16
    },
    {
      "start": 36.295,
      "end": 39.36,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in mighty prayer and supplication for my own soul;",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 17
    },
    {
      "start": 39.54,
      "end": 42.048,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all the day long did I cry to him;",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 18
    },
    {
      "start": 42.228,
      "end": 44.039,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "yes, and when the night came",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 19
    },
    {
      "start": 44.219,
      "end": 46.123,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I did still raise my voice high",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 20
    },
    {
      "start": 46.303,
      "end": 47.789,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it reached the heavens.",
      "verse": "1:4",
      "lineIndex": 21
    },
    {
      "start": 48.469,
      "end": 50.605,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there came a voice to me, saying:",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 23
    },
    {
      "start": 50.785,
      "end": 52.968,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Enos, your sins are forgiven you,",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 24
    },
    {
      "start": 53.148,
      "end": 54.681,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and you shall be blessed.",
      "verse": "1:5",
      "lineIndex": 25
    },
    {
      "start": 55.361,
      "end": 58.101,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Enos, knew that God could not lie;",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 26
    },
    {
      "start": 58.281,
      "end": 59.953,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, my guilt was swept away.",
      "verse": "1:6",
      "lineIndex": 27
    },
    {
      "start": 60.633,
      "end": 62.583,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I said: Lord, how is it done?",
      "verse": "1:7",
      "lineIndex": 28
    },
    {
      "start": 63.263,
      "end": 64.656,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And he said to me:",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 30
    },
    {
      "start": 64.836,
      "end": 66.694,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Because of your faith in Christ,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 31
    },
    {
      "start": 66.874,
      "end": 69.475,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "whom you have never before heard nor seen.",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 32
    },
    {
      "start": 69.655,
      "end": 71.327,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And many years pass away",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 33
    },
    {
      "start": 71.507,
      "end": 74.34,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "before he shall manifest himself in the flesh;",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 34
    },
    {
      "start": 74.52,
      "end": 75.542,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, go,",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 35
    },
    {
      "start": 75.722,
      "end": 77.533,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "your faith has made you whole.",
      "verse": "1:8",
      "lineIndex": 36
    },
    {
      "start": 78.213,
      "end": 80.442,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Now, when I had heard these words",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 38
    },
    {
      "start": 80.622,
      "end": 84.802,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I began to feel a desire for the welfare of my brothers, the Nephites;",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 39
    },
    {
      "start": 84.982,
      "end": 87.861,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, I poured out my whole soul to God for them.",
      "verse": "1:9",
      "lineIndex": 40
    },
    {
      "start": 88.541,
      "end": 91.049,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And while I was thus struggling in the spirit,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 41
    },
    {
      "start": 91.229,
      "end": 94.712,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "behold, the voice of the Lord came into my mind again, saying:",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 42
    },
    {
      "start": 94.892,
      "end": 96.471,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will visit your brothers",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 43
    },
    {
      "start": 96.651,
      "end": 99.623,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "according to their diligence in keeping my commandments.",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 44
    },
    {
      "start": 99.803,
      "end": 101.707,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I have given to them this land,",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 45
    },
    {
      "start": 101.887,
      "end": 103.512,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it is a holy land;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 46
    },
    {
      "start": 103.692,
      "end": 104.992,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I curse it not",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 47
    },
    {
      "start": 105.172,
      "end": 107.308,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "except for the cause of iniquity;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 48
    },
    {
      "start": 107.488,
      "end": 111.389,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so, I will visit your brothers according as I have said;",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 49
    },
    {
      "start": 111.569,
      "end": 115.656,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their transgressions will I bring down with sorrow upon their own heads.",
      "verse": "1:10",
      "lineIndex": 50
    },
    {
      "start": 116.336,
      "end": 118.983,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after I, Enos, had heard these words,",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 51
    },
    {
      "start": 119.163,
      "end": 121.764,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "my faith began to be unshaken in the Lord;",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 52
    },
    {
      "start": 121.944,
      "end": 126.309,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I prayed to him with many long strugglings for my brothers, the Lamanites.",
      "verse": "1:11",
      "lineIndex": 53
    },
    {
      "start": 126.989,
      "end": 130.193,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then after I had prayed and labored with all diligence,",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 55
    },
    {
      "start": 130.373,
      "end": 131.766,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "the Lord said to me:",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 56
    },
    {
      "start": 131.946,
      "end": 134.547,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I will grant to you according to your desires,",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 57
    },
    {
      "start": 134.727,
      "end": 136.12,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "because of your faith.",
      "verse": "1:12",
      "lineIndex": 58
    },
    {
      "start": 136.8,
      "end": 140.376,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now behold, this was the desire which I desired of him\u2014",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 60
    },
    {
      "start": 140.556,
      "end": 142.181,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that if it should so be",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 61
    },
    {
      "start": 142.361,
      "end": 144.311,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that my people, the Nephites,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 62
    },
    {
      "start": 144.491,
      "end": 146.674,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "should fall into transgression,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 63
    },
    {
      "start": 146.854,
      "end": 148.804,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and by any means be destroyed,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 64
    },
    {
      "start": 148.984,
      "end": 151.492,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the Lamanites should not be destroyed,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 65
    },
    {
      "start": 151.672,
      "end": 155.387,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord God would preserve a record of my people, the Nephites;",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 66
    },
    {
      "start": 155.567,
      "end": 158.446,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "even if it so be by the power of his holy arm,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 67
    },
    {
      "start": 158.626,
      "end": 162.202,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that it might be brought forth at some future day to the Lamanites,",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 68
    },
    {
      "start": 162.382,
      "end": 164.89,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that, perhaps, they might be brought to salvation\u2014",
      "verse": "1:13",
      "lineIndex": 69
    },
    {
      "start": 165.57,
      "end": 168.217,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "For at the present our strugglings were vain",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 70
    },
    {
      "start": 168.397,
      "end": 170.533,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "in restoring them to the true faith.",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 71
    },
    {
      "start": 170.713,
      "end": 172.663,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And they swore in their wrath that,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 72
    },
    {
      "start": 172.843,
      "end": 174.19,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "if it were possible,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 73
    },
    {
      "start": 174.37,
      "end": 176.599,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "they would destroy our records and us,",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 74
    },
    {
      "start": 176.779,
      "end": 179.473,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and also all the traditions of our fathers.",
      "verse": "1:14",
      "lineIndex": 75
    },
    {
      "start": 180.153,
      "end": 181.221,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "So, I knowing",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 76
    },
    {
      "start": 181.401,
      "end": 184.187,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that the Lord God was able to preserve our records,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 77
    },
    {
      "start": 184.367,
      "end": 187.293,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I cried to him continually, for he had said to me:",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 78
    },
    {
      "start": 187.473,
      "end": 189.749,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Whatsoever thing you shall ask in faith,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 79
    },
    {
      "start": 189.929,
      "end": 192.762,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "believing that you shall receive in the name of Christ,",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 80
    },
    {
      "start": 192.942,
      "end": 194.289,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "you shall receive it.",
      "verse": "1:15",
      "lineIndex": 81
    },
    {
      "start": 194.969,
      "end": 196.269,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I had faith,",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 83
    },
    {
      "start": 196.449,
      "end": 197.889,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and I cried to God",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 84
    },
    {
      "start": 198.069,
      "end": 200.112,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he would preserve the records;",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 85
    },
    {
      "start": 200.292,
      "end": 201.871,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he covenanted with me",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 86
    },
    {
      "start": 202.051,
      "end": 206.184,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that he would bring them forth to the Lamanites in his own due time.",
      "verse": "1:16",
      "lineIndex": 87
    },
    {
      "start": 206.864,
      "end": 211.136,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I, Enos, knew it would be according to the covenant which he had made;",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 88
    },
    {
      "start": 211.316,
      "end": 212.709,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "so my soul rested.",
      "verse": "1:17",
      "lineIndex": 89
    },
    {
      "start": 213.389,
      "end": 214.875,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the Lord said to me:",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 90
    },
    {
      "start": 215.055,
      "end": 217.795,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Your fathers have also required of me this thing;",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 91
    },
    {
      "start": 217.975,
      "end": 221.179,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and it shall be done to them according to their faith;",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 92
    },
    {
      "start": 221.359,
      "end": 223.449,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for their faith was like to your.",
      "verse": "1:18",
      "lineIndex": 93
    },
    {
      "start": 224.129,
      "end": 227.658,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And now I, Enos, went about among the people of Nephi,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 95
    },
    {
      "start": 227.838,
      "end": 229.742,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "prophesying of things to come,",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 96
    },
    {
      "start": 229.922,
      "end": 233.173,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and testifying of the things which I had heard and seen.",
      "verse": "1:19",
      "lineIndex": 97
    },
    {
      "start": 233.853,
      "end": 237.847,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I bear record that the people of Nephi sought diligently",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 98
    },
    {
      "start": 238.027,
      "end": 241.324,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to restore the Lamanites to the true faith in God.",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 99
    },
    {
      "start": 241.504,
      "end": 243.129,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "But our labors were vain;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 100
    },
    {
      "start": 243.309,
      "end": 244.795,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "their hatred was fixed,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 101
    },
    {
      "start": 244.975,
      "end": 247.529,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were led by their evil nature",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 102
    },
    {
      "start": 247.709,
      "end": 251.981,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that they became wild, and ferocious, and a blood-thirsty people,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 103
    },
    {
      "start": 252.161,
      "end": 254.39,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "full of idolatry and filthiness;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 104
    },
    {
      "start": 254.57,
      "end": 257.681,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "feeding upon beasts of prey; dwelling in tents,",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 105
    },
    {
      "start": 257.861,
      "end": 260.183,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and wandering about in the wilderness",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 106
    },
    {
      "start": 260.363,
      "end": 263.892,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "with a short skin belt about their waist and their heads shaven;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 107
    },
    {
      "start": 264.072,
      "end": 268.112,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and their skill was in the bow, and in the cimeter, and the ax.",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 108
    },
    {
      "start": 268.292,
      "end": 271.403,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And many of them ate nothing save it was raw meat;",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 109
    },
    {
      "start": 271.583,
      "end": 274.369,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and they were continually seeking to destroy us.",
      "verse": "1:20",
      "lineIndex": 110
    },
    {
      "start": 275.049,
      "end": 277.743,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then the people of Nephi tilled the land,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 111
    },
    {
      "start": 277.923,
      "end": 280.477,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and raise all manner of grain, and of fruit,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 112
    },
    {
      "start": 280.657,
      "end": 282.143,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and flocks of herds,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 113
    },
    {
      "start": 282.323,
      "end": 285.249,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and flocks of all manner of cattle of every kind,",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 114
    },
    {
      "start": 285.429,
      "end": 288.494,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and goats, and wild goats, and also many horses.",
      "verse": "1:21",
      "lineIndex": 115
    },
    {
      "start": 289.174,
      "end": 291.496,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there were very many prophets among us.",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 116
    },
    {
      "start": 291.676,
      "end": 295.252,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And the people were a stiffnecked people, hard to understand.",
      "verse": "1:22",
      "lineIndex": 117
    },
    {
      "start": 295.932,
      "end": 298.765,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And there was nothing save it was great harshness,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 119
    },
    {
      "start": 298.945,
      "end": 303.775,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "preaching and prophesying of wars, and contentions, and destructions,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 120
    },
    {
      "start": 303.955,
      "end": 306.277,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and continually reminding them of death,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 121
    },
    {
      "start": 306.457,
      "end": 308.454,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the duration of eternity,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 122
    },
    {
      "start": 308.634,
      "end": 311.002,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and the judgments and the power of God,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 123
    },
    {
      "start": 311.182,
      "end": 314.015,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and all these things\u2014stirring them up continually",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 124
    },
    {
      "start": 314.195,
      "end": 316.378,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "to keep them in the fear of the Lord.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 125
    },
    {
      "start": 316.558,
      "end": 318.88,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "I say there was nothing short of these things,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 126
    },
    {
      "start": 319.06,
      "end": 321.196,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and very great plainness of speech,",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 127
    },
    {
      "start": 321.376,
      "end": 324.998,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "would keep them from going down speedily to destruction.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 128
    },
    {
      "start": 325.178,
      "end": 327.964,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And after this manner do I write concerning them.",
      "verse": "1:23",
      "lineIndex": 129
    },
    {
      "start": 328.644,
      "end": 333.009,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw wars between the Nephites and Lamanites in the course of my days.",
      "verse": "1:24",
      "lineIndex": 130
    },
    {
      "start": 333.689,
      "end": 335.5,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And then I began to be old,",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 131
    },
    {
      "start": 335.68,
      "end": 338.977,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and an hundred and seventy and nine years had passed away",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 132
    },
    {
      "start": 339.157,
      "end": 342.315,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "from the time that our father Lehi left Jerusalem.",
      "verse": "1:25",
      "lineIndex": 133
    },
    {
      "start": 342.995,
      "end": 345.781,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I saw that I must soon go down to my grave,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 134
    },
    {
      "start": 345.961,
      "end": 348.747,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "having been wrought upon by the power of God",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 135
    },
    {
      "start": 348.927,
      "end": 352.085,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "that I must preach and prophesy to this people,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 136
    },
    {
      "start": 352.265,
      "end": 356.212,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and declare the word according to the truth which is in Christ.",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 137
    },
    {
      "start": 356.392,
      "end": 358.76,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I have declared it in all my days,",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 138
    },
    {
      "start": 358.94,
      "end": 361.68,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and have rejoiced in it above that of the world.",
      "verse": "1:26",
      "lineIndex": 139
    },
    {
      "start": 362.36,
      "end": 364.728,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I soon go to the place of my rest,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 140
    },
    {
      "start": 364.908,
      "end": 366.626,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "which is with my Redeemer;",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 141
    },
    {
      "start": 366.806,
      "end": 369.128,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "for I know that in him I shall rest.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 142
    },
    {
      "start": 369.308,
      "end": 370.841,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "And I rejoice in the day",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 143
    },
    {
      "start": 371.021,
      "end": 373.482,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "when my mortal shall put on immortality,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 144
    },
    {
      "start": 373.662,
      "end": 375.566,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and shall stand before him;",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 145
    },
    {
      "start": 375.746,
      "end": 378.022,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "then shall I see his face with pleasure,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 146
    },
    {
      "start": 378.202,
      "end": 379.688,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "and he will say to me:",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 147
    },
    {
      "start": 379.868,
      "end": 381.308,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Come to me, you blessed,",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 148
    },
    {
      "start": 381.488,
      "end": 385.017,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "there is a place prepared for you in the mansions of my Father.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 149
    },
    {
      "start": 385.197,
      "end": 386.033,
      "type": "line",
      "text": "Amen.",
      "verse": "1:27",
      "lineIndex": 150
    }
  ]
}